Subject: Access Issues with AWS Websites
Description: We are currently experiencing an issue with accessing the AWS website. While the site itself loads and is not being blocked, the content or data on the page fails to load properly. Instead, we are receiving an error message when attempting to interact with certain services or sections of the site.
What_We_Know__c:
09.05
- the customer is experiencing an issue with accessing the AWS website. While the site itself loads and is not being blocked, the content or data on the page fails to load properly. Instead, we are receiving an error message when attempting to interact with certain services or sections of the site.
- asked for more details and screenshots
- asked the customer for their availability

13.05
- 5.9.4.1 server version
- sent them the test build which was created for 439988
- test build no: 6.2.4.0125
- test build was not connecting to the server

- need to check the logs with T2
- told the customer text files cause false positives when browsing websites as text files are continually uploaded and downloaded during browsing
